title: Mobstar Script 2008
description:
Ranking script for the MMORPG Mobstar.
This script wil rank your account to assassin within 2 days, Local Boss within 3 days.

Description about the game below.

Also checkfor an example about the ranking script.
Mobstar is an addictive online game based on the treacherous world of the mafia, where thousands of players immerse themselves in the role of an international criminal. You begin Mobstar as lowly thug, doing drug runs from one of fifteen starting locations, such as Australia, Brazil, Great Britain and USA. Climb the criminal career ladder by accumulating wealth and status, and achieve the ultimate goal of becoming Godfather!

    * Multiplayer strategy game, with strong emphasis on social interaction.
    * Fun gambling games including roulette, blackjack and betting pools.
    * No installation required! You only need your browser to play.

The basic game is completely free! For a small annual fee we'll give you access to advanced features, including the ability to steal vehicles, kill other players and start your own crew.


Home Page - http://www.mobstar.cc
